------------------------------------------------------------
BASE STATS

STR . strength
INT . intelligence

REF . reflex
ACC . accuracy

CON . constitution
KNO . knowledge

------------------------------------------------------------
COMBAT STATS

ATK . attack = STR and ACC
DEF . defense = STR and REF

MATK . magical attack = INT and ACC
MDEF . magical defense = INT and REF

HP . health points = CON
FLOW . flow = KNO

INIT . initiative = STR and CON and INT and KNO
